{
  "stem": "13313.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the-- the secular teachers, the Flemish or French teachers, were whipping up a lot of a nationalism among their own students.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- so it turned out that when we went at recess, we did not really play.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We divide in two camps, and we fought each other.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were re-enacting the historic battles between the-- the Flemish peasantry and the French-- and the French occupants-- occupiers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So this was quite something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And really, it was a perfect example of how we can brainwash children.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So here we were, these little Jewish kids who had nothing to do with this-- with this particular history, and we were fighting out the-- the-- the Flemish-French battles in the courtyard.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, one of the kids had to be escorted home because the other ones would go after them.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was really violent.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was in grade one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the next grade, I'm in there from the other side.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All of a sudden, I was switching camps and fighting the other battle of the French against the Flemish.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was quite-- quite traumatic how I kept changing sides, because, you know, my father didn't know this was going to happen.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that's a-- a recollection.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The positive thing is that as a result I consider both Flemish, which is a Dutch dialect, and French my two mother tongues.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I never lost them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I'm quite fluent in both.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was a positive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, a few.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would say these are my two mother tongues.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then when I managed to go to high school after the war, we had actually four languages of instruction.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were three compulsory languages, which was the Dutch, French, and English.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we had German as an optional language, which was the fourth.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
